      "rationale": "Screw geometry derived from CMM measurements of production parts (n=3 screws per lot). Material moduli and Poisson ratios from lot-specific coupon tests. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (1000 samples); 95th-percentile QoI bounds reported alongside nominal predictions. All inputs traceable to calibrated measurement records."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
