      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single displacement rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717 protocol. Although this rate is standard and clinically representative, only one test condition was evaluated. The required Gradation 3 calls for multi-condition coverage; achieved level is 2. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of the protocol."
