      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement using combined model and experimental uncertainty. All E/uval values < 1.96 and all relative errors < 10%. Acceptance bounds were pre-registered in the validation plan prior to experimental data unblinding. Required level met."
