      "rationale": "The assessment team determined that this factor does not apply to the present COU because the validation activity is co-extensive with the COU itself — the FEA model is validated against the exact test configuration (ASTM F1717, non-cannulated 7.5 mm construct) that defines the COU. No extrapolation beyond the validated scenario is claimed, making a separate relevance assessment superfluous. Accordingly, formal scoring of required and achieved levels was not performed. The team notes this position without invoking a 'not-applicable' classification, as the factor was considered but judged to require no further quantitative grading given the direct correspondence between validation scope and COU scope."
